<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1976423-i-am-not-super-familiar-with-the-details">I am not super familiar with the details of Chinese history in this time period. Would I get more out of this book if I were to learn more before reading it? Or does the book put all the personal events in a greater historic context?</a>
</div>
