          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50066399-diane-in-australia?shelf=nonfiction-biography">nonfiction-biography</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50066399-diane-in-australia?shelf=nonfiction-autobiography">nonfiction-autobiography</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3415228675" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1780423900477310527">I enjoy books that let me see history from a private, and very personal, point of view. This book does that. Mind-boggling what a country, and a people, can endure.<br/><br/>4 Stars = Outstanding. It definitely held my interest.<br/><br/>(My apologies for such a short review. I&apos;m struggling with a few things, at the moment, and just can&apos;t seem to find the presence of mind to write longer reviews.)</span>
