        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1584180568" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8917427258115629471">This is a whirlwind story, focusing around the tragedy of China throughout much of the last century through three generations of women. The greatest havoc is wrought by Mao Zedong and his wife, particularly through his Cultural Revolution in which young people are pitched against teachers, intellectuals and artists in a highly successful attempt to divide and rule. It&apos;s like Lord of the Flies meets real life. Read this book, especially if you don&apos;t know much about China - it&apos;s an education.</span>
  <span id="freeText8917427258115629471" style="display:none">This is a whirlwind story, focusing around the tragedy of China throughout much of the last century through three generations of women. The greatest havoc is wrought by Mao Zedong and his wife, particularly through his Cultural Revolution in which young people are pitched against teachers, intellectuals and artists in a highly successful attempt to divide and rule. It's like Lord of the Flies meets real life. Read this book, especially if you don't know much about China - it's an education.</span>
