<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28595552-kong-yiji"><img alt="Kong Yiji: Bilingual Edition, English and Chinese 孔乙己 (Lu Xun 鲁迅 Bilingual Study Series Book 2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1453125352l/28595552._SX98_.jpg" />
